    "    (\"☐ 并发控制\", \"设置 max_concurrency 和 recursion_limit\", \"HIGH\"),\n",
    "    (\"☐ Langfuse 监控\", \"配置 Trace、Score、Dataset、Tags\", \"HIGH\"),\n",
    "    (\"☐ Prompt 版本管理\", \"YAML 本地版本 + Langfuse Hub 同步 + production 标签\", \"HIGH\"),\n",
    "    (\"☐ 容错降级\", \"Redis 故障→Postgres→Memory；LLM 故障→轻量模型→缓存\", \"CRITICAL\"),\n",
    "    (\"☐ 异步任务\", \"Celery 队列处理耗时任务，避免阻塞主线程\", \"MEDIUM\"),\n",
    "    (\"☐ 流式输出\", \"ProductionStreamWriter + DebugPrinter 调试工具\", \"MEDIUM\"),\n",
